{"id":["107831879234996344"],"username":["MediaActivist"],"acct":["MediaActivist@kolektiva.social"],"display_name":["Jay Baker (they/he)"],"locked":[false],"bot":[false],"discoverable":[true],"indexable":[false],"group":[false],"created_at":["2020-09-20T00:00:00.000Z"],"note":["<p>Long-time guerrilla journalist and documentarian (ex-<a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/IndyMedia\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>IndyMedia<\/span><\/a>) – powered largely by <a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/Linux\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Linux<\/span><\/a> (and coffee!) in the UK’s Steel City. <\/p><p><a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/Freelancer\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Freelancer<\/span><\/a> and unpaid carer for partner with <a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/LongCovid\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>LongCovid<\/span><\/a>. Hire me you cowards!<\/p><p>Part tech geek. Part pop culture nerd. 100% punk.<\/p><p>Avatar: Me smiling awkwardly at the camera. Banner: Me again, documenting a protest with a video camera.<\/p><p>Searchable via <a href=\"https://tootfinder.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" translate=\"no\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://<\/span><span class=\"\">tootfinder.ch/<\/span><span class=\"invisible\"><\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/tfr\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>tfr<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/fedi22\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>fedi22<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://kolektiva.social/tags/queer\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>queer<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"htt